44function CTASelectionSet()
45{
46    global $mpd_features,$session_dir,$CTAselectionset_infofile,$current_period,$adaptation_set_template, $opfile, $string_info, $progress_xml, $progress_report,
47            $MediaProfDatabase,$current_period;
48    $opfile="";
49    
50    
51    if(!($opfile = open_file($session_dir. '/Period' . $current_period . '/' . $CTAselectionset_infofile . '.txt', 'w'))){
52        echo "Error opening/creating Selection Set conformance check file: "."./SelectionSet_infofile_ctawave.txt";
53        return;
54    }
55    //fprintf($opfile, "**Selection Set conformance check: \n\n");
56    $adapts = $mpd_features['Period'][$current_period]['AdaptationSet'];
57    $result=CTACheckSelectionSet(sizeof($adapts),$session_dir,$adaptation_set_template,$opfile,$current_period);
58    $infoResult=CTACheckSingleInitSwSet(sizeof($adapts),$session_dir,$adaptation_set_template);
59    fwrite($opfile,$infoResult);
60    fclose($opfile);
61    
62    $searchfiles = file_get_contents($session_dir.'/Period'.$current_period.'/'.$CTAselectionset_infofile.'.txt');
63    if(strpos($searchfiles, "CTAWAVE check violated") !== FALSE){
64        $progress_xml->Results[0]->Period[$current_period]->addChild('CTAWAVESelectionSet', 'error');
65        $file_error[] = $session_dir.'/Period'.$current_period.'/'.$CTAselectionset_infofile.'.html';
66    }
67    elseif(strpos($searchfiles, "Warning") !== FALSE || strpos($searchfiles, "WARNING") !== FALSE){
68        $progress_xml->Results[0]->Period[$current_period]->addChild('CTAWAVESelectionSet', 'warning');
69        $file_error[] = $session_dir.'/Period'.$current_period.'/'.$CTAselectionset_infofile.'.html';
70    }
71    else{
72        $progress_xml->Results[0]->Period[$current_period]->addChild('CTAWAVESelectionSet', 'noerror');
73        $file_error[] = "noerror";
74    }
75    $progress_xml->asXml(trim($session_dir . '/' . $progress_report));
76    tabulateResults($session_dir.'/Period'.$current_period.'/'.$CTAselectionset_infofile.'.txt', 'Cross');
77    print_console($session_dir.'/Period'.$current_period.'/'.$CTAselectionset_infofile.'.txt', "Period " . ($current_period+1) . " CTA WAVE Selection Set Results");
78}

194function getMediaProfile($xml,$handler_type,$repCount, $adaptCount,$opfile)
195{
196    global $MediaProfileAttributesVideo, $MediaProfileAttributesAudio, $MediaProfileAttributesSubtitle;
197    $compatible_brands=$xml->getElementsByTagName("ftyp")->item(0)->getAttribute("compatible_brands");
198    if($handler_type=='vide')
199    {
200        $xml_MPParameters= $MediaProfileAttributesVideo;
201        $videSampleDes=$xml->getElementsByTagName("vide_sampledescription")->item(0);
202        $sdType=$videSampleDes->getAttribute("sdType");
203        if($sdType=='avc1' || $sdType=='avc3')
204        {
205            $xml_MPParameters['codec']="AVC";
206            $nal_unit=$xml->getElementsByTagName("NALUnit");
207            if($nal_unit->length==0){
208               $errorMsg= "###CTAWAVE check violated: WAVE Content Spec 2018Ed-Section 4.2.1: 'Each WAVE Video Media Profile SHALL conform to normative ref. listed in Table 1',AVC media profiles conformance failed.  NAL unit not found in the sample description and identification of the exact media profile not possible for track ".$repCount." of SwitchingSet ".$adaptCount.". \n";      
209               return ["unknown", $errorMsg];
210            }
211            else{
212                for($nal_count=0;$nal_count<$nal_unit->length;$nal_count++)
213                {
214                    if($nal_unit->item($nal_count)->getAttribute("nal_type")=="0x07")
215                    {    $sps_unit=$nal_count;
216                         break;
217                    }  
218                }
219            }
220          $comment=$nal_unit->item($sps_unit)->getElementsByTagName("comment")->item(0);  
221          $xml_MPParameters['profile']=$comment->getAttribute("profile");
222          $xml_MPParameters['level']=(float)($comment->getAttribute("level_idc"))/10;
223          $xml_MPParameters['width']=$videSampleDes->getAttribute("width"); 
224          $xml_MPParameters['height']=$videSampleDes->getAttribute("height"); 
225          if($comment->getAttribute("vui_parameters_present_flag")=="0x1")
226          {
227              if($comment->getAttribute("video_signal_type_present_flag")=="0x1")
228              {
229                  if($comment->getAttribute("colour_description_present_flag")=="0x1")
230                  {
231                    $xml_MPParameters['color_primaries']=$comment->getAttribute("colour_primaries");
232                    $xml_MPParameters['transfer_char']=$comment->getAttribute("transfer_characteristics");
233                    $xml_MPParameters['matrix_coeff']=$comment->getAttribute("matrix_coefficients");
234                  }
235                  elseif($comment->getAttribute("colour_description_present_flag")=="0x0")
236                  {
237                    $xml_MPParameters['color_primaries']="0x1";
238                    $xml_MPParameters['transfer_char']="0x1";
239                    $xml_MPParameters['matrix_coeff']="0x1";
240                  }
241              }
242              if($comment->getAttribute("timing_info_present_flag")=="0x1" )
243              {
244                  $num_units_in_tick=$comment->getAttribute("num_units_in_tick");
245                  $time_scale=$comment->getAttribute("time_scale");
246                  $xml_MPParameters['framerate']=$time_scale/(2*$num_units_in_tick);
247              }
248          }
249          $brand_pos=strpos($compatible_brands,"cfsd") || strpos($compatible_brands,"cfhd");
250          if($brand_pos!==False){
251              if(strpos($compatible_brands,"cfsd")!==FALSE)
252                $xml_MPParameters['brand']="cfsd";
253              if(strpos($compatible_brands,"cfhd")!==FALSE)
254                $xml_MPParameters['brand']="cfhd";
255          }
256                  
257        }
258        else if($sdType=='hev1' || $sdType=='hvc1')
259        {
260            $xml_MPParameters['codec']="HEVC";
261            $hvcC=$xml->getElementsByTagName("hvcC");
262            if($hvcC->length>0)
263            {
264                $hvcC=$xml->getElementsByTagName("hvcC")->item(0);
265                if(($hvcC->getAttribute("profile_idc")=="1") || ($hvcC->getAttribute("compatibility_flag_1"))=="1")
266                    $profile="Main";
267                elseif(($hvcC->getAttribute("profile_idc")=="2") || ($hvcC->getAttribute("compatibility_flag_2"))=="1")
268                    $profile="Main10";
269                else
270                    $profile="Other";
271
272                $tier=$hvcC->getAttribute("tier_flag");
273                $xml_MPParameters['tier']=$tier;//Tier=0 is the main-tier.
274                $xml_MPParameters['profile']=$profile;
275                $xml_MPParameters['level']=(float)($hvcC->getAttribute("level_idc"))/30; //HEVC std defines level_idc is 30 times of actual level number.
276            }
277            $xml_MPParameters['width']=$videSampleDes->getAttribute("width"); 
278            $xml_MPParameters['height']=$videSampleDes->getAttribute("height");

280            if($nal_unit->length==0){
281                $errorMsg= "###CTAWAVE check violated: WAVE Content Spec 2018Ed-Section 4.2.1: 'Each WAVE Video Media Profile SHALL conform to normative ref. listed in Table 1',HEVC media profiles conformance failed.  NAL unit not found in the sample description and identification of the exact media profile not possible for track ".$repCount." of SwitchingSet ".$adaptCount.". \n";      
282                return ["unknown", $errorMsg];
283            }
284            else{
285                for($nal_count=0;$nal_count<$nal_unit->length;$nal_count++)
286                {
287                    if($nal_unit->item($nal_count)->getAttribute("nal_unit_type")=="33")
288                    {    $sps_unit=$nal_count;
289                         break;
290                    }  
291                }
292            } 
293            $sps=$nal_unit->item($sps_unit);
294            if($sps->getAttribute("vui_parameters_present_flag")=="1")
295            {
296              if($sps->getAttribute("video_signal_type_present_flag")=="1")
297              {
298                  if($sps->getAttribute("colour_description_present_flag")=="1")
299                  {
300                    $xml_MPParameters['color_primaries']=$sps->getAttribute("colour_primaries");
301                    $xml_MPParameters['transfer_char']=$sps->getAttribute("transfer_characteristics");
302                    $xml_MPParameters['matrix_coeff']=$sps->getAttribute("matrix_coeffs");
303                  }
304                  elseif($sps->getAttribute("colour_description_present_flag")=="0")
305                  {
306                    $xml_MPParameters['color_primaries']="1";
307                    $xml_MPParameters['transfer_char']="1";
308                    $xml_MPParameters['matrix_coeff']="1";
309                  }
310              }
311              if($sps->getAttribute("vui_timing_info_present_flag")=="1" )
312              {
313                  $num_units_in_tick=$sps->getAttribute("vui_num_units_in_tick");
314                  $time_scale=$sps->getAttribute("vui_time_scale");
315                  $xml_MPParameters['framerate']=$time_scale/($num_units_in_tick);
316              }
317            }
318            $brand_pos=strpos($compatible_brands,"chh1") || strpos($compatible_brands,"cud1")||strpos($compatible_brands,"clg1")||strpos($compatible_brands,"chd1");
319            if($brand_pos!==False){
